</style><p>此外，在毕业分发当天，还将公开一张写有“<em>我很畏缩，但我很</em>自由……”的图像的缩略图。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="qme" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/ZnQOsUrNBE">https://t.co/ZnQOsUrNBE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Otsuzura?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Otsuzura</a> <a href="https://t.co/dgtM6rBPbg">pic.twitter.com/dgtM6rBPbg</a></p> — Azura Cecillia 已退出。(@Azura_Cecillia) <a href="https://twitter.com/Azura_Cecillia/status/1693196811119517716?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 20 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><p>此次阿祖拉·塞西莉亚被指定为缩略图的原因尚不清楚，但近年来，海外观众和粉丝对组合和公司的人才活动环境提出了批评，除此之外，还有一些对公司的不满。从各位艺人的现状来看，阿祖拉·塞西莉亚在最终交付前也间接表现出了“某种想法”，据推测， </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="阿祖拉·塞西莉亚的毕业直播" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/e1k0YhJnmpU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/Azura_Cecilia/status/1693295737386467361 </div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ziEXSx7zOZ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/">Idol 将 75% 的收入返还给旗下 VTuber 不寻常披露背后的背景</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbo